<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَفْسِيرُ سُورَةِ الْبَقَرَة<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{ذَلِكَ الْكِتَابُ لَا رَيْبَ , فِيهِ هُدًى لِلْمُتَّقِينَ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٩ص١٥٤:</span> قَالَ مَعْمَرٌ: <span class="c3">{ذَلِكَ الكِتَابُ}</span>: <span class="c1">" هَذَا القُرْآنُ "</span> ,<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{لَا رَيْبَ}</span>: <span class="c1">" لَا شَكَّ "</span>،<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{هُدًى لِلْمُتَّقِينَ}</span>: <span class="c1">" بَيَانٌ وَدِلَالَةٌ "</span>،<span class="c5"> كَقَوْلِهِ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{ذَلِكُمْ حُكْمُ اللهِ}</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span>: <span class="c1">" هَذَا حُكْمُ اللهِ "</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [البقرة: ٢]<br>(٢) [الممتحنة: ١٠]</p> </div>